node.text: 100% honest with you all I hate giveaways. Every single one seems the same, and they’re usually some truck that’s so modified or clapped you can’t even use it. But this one does actually interest me because it’s not corny and you can make hella money with it. Plus it’ll last you a long time. This whole construction rig will be given away soon and it ends Sunday night. All you have to do is buy anything from @ownbosssupplyco with my code Whistlindiesel for money off your order. The apparel is actually pretty cool as well. You’re automatically entered by making a purchase. 2017 platinum dually, 25ft load trail, Cat 287D skid steer.

I’ll let it slide but next time you have to realize the meet and greet comes first. Also I followed you home. And took videos of you mowing the lawn. Sincerely, Youre bigest fan

node.text: FOR SALE. 2021 Avalanche 44ft 2 bed 2 bath house on wheels. Honestly I feel bad for whoever needs a 5th wheel and hasn’t seen this post because they’re losing $20k if they buy a different one. $53k. Model is 390DS. $2k deposit holds it for one week. Located near Nashville TN. Only needs your own couch and table installed. The stock ones were removed for a full size couch.

node.text: Just letting everyone know I’ve offered 5+ squatted truck owners what they were asking for their chromosomobiles and they all backed out on the sale when it was actually time to make 5X KBB value on a vehicle that’s not worth it’s value in scrap. Otherwise you’d have squatted truck videos and some souvenirs by now :)))) If a squatted truck owner is posting saying I’m buying their truck, just know I accepted and they were too pu$$ to go through with it.

node.text: These things are so freaking fun to use for obstacle courses. Plus I have free power after tapping into them. People are telling me not to build my shop near them though because there’s en electromagnetic field or something lol. Someone explain so I know if I need to line my shop with led blankets.
